moves.name: Absorb
moves.battle_effect: A nutrient-draining attack. The user's HP is restored by half the damage taken by the target.
moves.secondary_effect: User recovers half the damage inflicted.

moves.name: Acid
moves.battle_effect: The opposing team is attacked with a spray of harsh acid. The acid may also lower the targets' Sp. Def stats.
moves.secondary_effect: May lower opponent's SP. DEF one stage.

moves.name: Acid Armor
moves.battle_effect: The user alters its cellular structure to liquefy itself, sharply raising its Defense stat.

moves.name: Acid Spray
moves.battle_effect: The user spits fluid that works to melt the target. This harshly reduces the target's Sp. Def stat.
moves.secondary_effect: Lowers opponent's SP. DEF two stages.

moves.name: Acrobatics
moves.battle_effect: The user nimbly strikes the target. If the user is not holding an item, this attack inflicts massive damage.
moves.secondary_effect: Increases damage by 100% if user is not holding an item.

moves.name: Acupressure
moves.battle_effect: The user applies pressure to stress points, sharply boosting one of its stats.
moves.secondary_effect: Raises one of the user's stats randomly by two stages.

moves.name: Aerial Ace
moves.battle_effect: The user confounds the target with speed, then slashes. The attack lands without fail.

moves.name: Aeroblast
moves.battle_effect: A vortex of air is shot at the target to inflict damage. Critical hits land more easily.

moves.name: After You
moves.battle_effect: The user helps the target and makes it use its move right after the user.

moves.name: Agility
moves.battle_effect: The user relaxes and lightens its body to move faster. It sharply boosts the Speed stat.
